  "instructions": [
    "Boil the glutinous rice in chicken broth for about 30 minutes or until cooked.",
    "Prepare quail eggs by cracking each one and separating the yolks into a bowl.",
    "Season the yolk with salt. Fry the A Oli meat slices on high heat.",
    "Heat olive oil in a wok over medium-high heat, add minced ginger and stir-fry for 30 seconds.",
    "Add cooked quail eggs and A Oli to the wok; toss gently until everything is well combined.",
